deployment.message:
Fix: Use correct TypeScript package in build command
- Change from 'npx tsc' which installs wrong package (tsc@2.0.4) - Use 'node_modules/.bin/tsc' to run installed typescript - Fallback to 'npx typescript' if node_modules version fails - This ensures correct TypeScript compiler (5.3.3) is used
